  "description": "<p><strong>Introductions:</strong><br/>Your family will have a wonderful time with this large outdoor canopy. With a durable, hard canopy and thick, sturdy posts, this canopy is truly the ultimate in practicality and convenience. It comes with a carrying bag so that you can easily bring the convenient gazebo anywhere as a quick, sun-coverage solution. The canopy top also wear silver coating, which is UV-resistant and waterproof. The thicker and more durable powder-coated steel frame features pre-drilled holes so you can anchor it if desired. Set it up on your lawn or on your patio, or take it during camping, and get ready to enjoy delightful outdoor life!</p>\n <p><strong>Features:</strong><br/>1. Enough space to offer 25 sq. ft. of shade for multiple places<br/>2. Come with a carrying bag to collect and move easily<br/>3. The canopy top to be UV Resistant, waterproof and air-circulated<br/>4. Durable powder-coated and sturdy steel frame with pre-drilled holes in feet to anchor<br/>5. Adjustable legs: 3 height positions for your choice&nbsp;</p>\n <p><strong>Specifications:</strong><br/>1. Material: 420D Oxford fabric and metal<br/>2. Color: White top canopy and White frame<br/>3. Overall Dimensions: (5'X5'X7.9') / (150X150X240)cm (LxWxH)<br/>4. Weight: 17.6 lbs / 7.9 kg<br/>5. Waterproof: Yes</p>\n <p><strong>Packages Includes:</strong><br/>1 x Gazebo<br/>1 x Assembling Instructions</p>\n <p><strong>NOTE:&nbsp;</strong><br/>1. Keep the canopy away from fire!<br/>2. Please do not use the canopy in heavy rain or against strong wind!</p>\n <p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/2e76d5e9-278d-4fe1-b1c7-18d41013258f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/b1e92087-c9b2-4cbe-95c6-72a4cc3d309b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/5e63fa64-078f-4772-b4b1-9487ea103881.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img